          "date": "2025-07-25 00:57:27+00:00",
          "body": "<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\r\n<style type=\"text/css\" style=\"display:none;\"> P {margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;} </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" class=\"elementToProof\">\r\nI am one of many long-term NRA members who were aware of the corruption in our organization.&nbsp; Please continue to keep us informed in regards to the past mistakes made and how you are ensuring that they will never reoccur. I must be honest in that I still have\r\n some distrust in the NRA however your blunt honesty is making me reevaluate my future support. As a retired physician I am very generous to organizations I have confidence in and you are rein stilling my confidence in the NRA that my future donations will\r\n be used in an appropriate manor.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" class=\"elementToProof\">\r\n<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" class=\"elementToProof\">\r\nDennis Raphael MD</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" class=\"elementToProof\">\r\nmember #5507013</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n"
