          "sender": "wadedouglas42@gmail.com",
          "to": [
              "President@NRADirector.com"
          ],
          "date": "2025-07-24 01:04:42+00:00",
          "body": "I’m a life member of the NRA, and have been supportive of the defense of the second amendment. But in the past, the NRA fought common-sense gun-safety proposals always as a “slippery slope.” That hurt the NRA with the general public as being unreasonable."
